{"tid":2071764,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【難題】到底你寧願日日落雨定日日帶口罩？","createTime":"2020-06-20T05:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T09:19:31.000Z","uid":38177,"like":65,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd410091e51cae13f3148b5722607454bc02022","tid":2071764,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"日日落雨好似天氣之子咁，有時可能水浸，間中天晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但長時間落雨，每日出門都要日日帶傘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39sHBvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39sHBvQ.jpg&h=bdc00744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晾衫唔洗諗，日日洗衣機乾衣啦<br />\n<br />\n可以去旅行，可以去各國食好野，不過都要落雨要帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一入室內就無事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶口罩就好似而家咁<br />\n<br />\n日日焗撚住塊面，又出汗，又爆瘡，抖唔到氣，頭都暈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbMUsEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbMUsEy.jpg&h=79996ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返工又要帶，出街又要帶，又唔可以出國旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過就好撚好天，好撚曬，沙灘，游水都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vuo0odU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuo0odU.jpg&h=63a531f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">落雨，帶遮</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">疫症，帶口罩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c94503cb100c97fa7727edf44d8a2b0d4354801","tid":2071764,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"自己正評先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04944fea6d35da4d5503d5faf